<item>
            <title>[DOXIA-59] Doxia creates files with inconsistent new lines</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DOXIA-59</link>
                <project id="12317230" key="DOXIA">Maven Doxia (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It uses \n instead of System.getProperty( line.separator );&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12801521">DOXIA-59</key>
            <summary>Doxia creates files with inconsistent new lines</summary>
